channel.title: A bunch of the Falador Objects list =)
channel.description:
[b][size=15pt]Please post feedback ;)[/size][/b]
I made a list of a bunch of Falador Objects. They are around the 11000s, because the updated Falador is higher than 9999. A regular MoparScape cache (317) can hold it, so dont worry. Also, IF youre using this, Try ID Number'11705', because it is dirt! It works, as long as you use the Replacefloor void. Also, IDs 11691-11686 are white walls. Im so happy, because the whole perpose of this was to find the white wall id. And now I have them :D. Enjoy this!
~Lin
Note:The list is in an attatchment at the bottom.
